<div class="post-headline">		<h2>			
			<a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/2011/11/11/how-to-free-your-work-video/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to How To Free Your Work video">How To Free Your Work video</a></h2>
		</div>

<div class="post-bodycopy clearfix"><p><iframe src="http://player.vimeo.com/video/30856482" width="500" height="281" frameborder="0" webkitAllowFullScreen allowFullScreen></iframe><br />
Here at last is the video from my first How To Free Your Work workshop, given at NY Foundation for the Arts in Brooklyn, October 5 2011. You can get all the information contained herein as easy-to-read instructions at <a href="http://questioncopyright.org/how_to_free_your_work">QuestionCopyright.org</a>. If you want me to give a workshop like this to your group, please <a href="http://www.ninapaley.com/images/nospam.jpg">contact me</a>.</p>
