<div class="post-footer">March 26th, 2011 |  Category: <a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/category/advice/" title="View all posts in advice" rel="category tag">advice</a>, <a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/category/awesome/" title="View all posts in awesome" rel="category tag">awesome</a>, <a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/category/copyleft/" title="View all posts in copyleft" rel="category tag">copyleft</a>, <a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/category/copywrong/" title="View all posts in copywrong" rel="category tag">copywrong</a>, <a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/category/creativity/" title="View all posts in creativity" rel="category tag">creativity</a>, <a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/category/free-culture/" title="View all posts in Free Culture" rel="category tag">Free Culture</a>, <a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/category/heresy/" title="View all posts in heresy" rel="category tag">heresy</a>, <a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/category/law/" title="View all posts in Law" rel="category tag">Law</a>, <a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/category/philosophy/" title="View all posts in philosophy" rel="category tag">philosophy</a>, <a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/category/speaking/" title="View all posts in speaking" rel="category tag">speaking</a>, <a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/category/the-interwebs/" title="View all posts in the interwebs" rel="category tag">the interwebs</a> | <a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/2011/03/26/i-am-awesome/#comments" class="comments-link"  title="Comment on I am awesome">13 comments</a> </div>
