<div class="post-headline">		<h2>			
			<a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/2010/05/03/frederick-douglass-is-always-relevant/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to Frederick Douglass is always relevant">Frederick Douglass is always relevant</a></h2>
		</div>

<div class="post-bodycopy clearfix"><p>&#8220;Find out just what people will submit to, and you have found out the exact amount of injustice and wrong which will be imposed upon them; and these will continue until they are resisted with either words or blows, or with both. The limits of tyrants are prescribed by the endurance of those whom they oppress.&#8221; &#8212; <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Frederick_Douglass" target="_blank">Frederick Douglass</a>, August 4, 1857 (via <a href="http://www.freesoftwaremagazine.com/user/5" target="_blank">Terry Hancock</a>)</p>
<div class="plus-one-wrap"><g:plusone href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/2010/05/03/frederick-douglass-is-always-relevant/"></g:plusone></div><div class="addtoany_share_save_container"><div class="a2a_kit a2a_kit_size_32 a2a_target addtoany_list" id="wpa2a_11"><a class="a2a_dd addtoany_share_save" href="http://www.addtoany.com/share_save" style="background:url(http://blog.ninapaley.com/wp-content/plugins/add-to-any/favicon.png) no-repeat scroll 4px 0px !important;padding:0 0 0 25px;display:inline-block;height:16px;vertical-align:middle">Share/Bookmark</a></div></div><p class="wp-flattr-button"><a class="FlattrButton" style="display:none;" href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/2010/05/03/frederick-douglass-is-always-relevant/" title=" Frederick Douglass is always relevant" rev="flattr;uid:ninapaley;language:en_GB;category:text;tags:blog;button:compact;">&#8220;Find out just what people will submit to, and you have found out the exact amount of injustice and wrong which will be imposed upon them; and these will continue...</a></p></div>

<div class="post-footer">May 3rd, 2010 |  Category: <a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/category/advice/" title="View all posts in advice" rel="category tag">advice</a>, <a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/category/freedom/" title="View all posts in freedom" rel="category tag">freedom</a>, <a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/category/philosophy/" title="View all posts in philosophy" rel="category tag">philosophy</a> | <a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/2010/05/03/frederick-douglass-is-always-relevant/#comments" class="comments-link"  title="Comment on Frederick Douglass is always relevant">9 comments</a> </div>
